{"tid":408762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓決定向北韓提供800萬美元人道援助","createTime":"2017-09-21T13:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T11:50:36.000Z","uid":4783,"like":7,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7c7c63995489e7d71c0604e49b1030bc7796a9","tid":408762,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"21.09.2017 13:50<br />\n南韓政府決定向北韓提供八百萬美元的人道援助，但未確定具體落實時間，南韓統一部表示將考慮兩韓關係後再決定。今次是文在寅政府上台後，南韓首次對北韓提供人道援助。<br />\n<br />\n南韓政府計劃，向世界糧食計劃署提供四百五十萬美元的兒童和孕婦營養食品，及向聯合國兒童基金會提供三百五十萬美元的兒童及孕婦醫藥品和營養劑等，轉交北韓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=965660&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D965660%26csid%3D261_367&d=mFNsu6F1qPnfRaHwWYJvpDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fdc0587d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=965660&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"2ce08323d25fbc46362f1ab2b893af01e1314d31","tid":408762,"uid":7699,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>21.09.2017 13:50<br />\n南韓政府決定向北韓提供八百萬美元的人道援助，但未確定具體落實時間，南韓統一部表示將考慮兩韓關係後再決定。今次是文在寅政府上台後，南韓首次對北韓提供人道援助。<br />\n<br />\n南韓政府計劃，向世界糧食計劃署提供四百五十萬美元的兒童和孕婦營養食品，及向聯合國兒童基金會提供三百五十萬美元的兒童及孕婦醫藥品和營養劑等，轉交北韓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=965660&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D965660%26csid%3D261_367&d=mFNsu6F1qPnfRaHwWYJvpDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fdc0587d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=965660&amp;csid=261_367</a></blockquote><br />\n金仔又收保護費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb303ba29e81bec576b004e612a394feeb99cd9","tid":408762,"uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"r